  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><em><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListTypes_ctl110_LabelType\">You know how dragons move and how they perceive body language.</span></em></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Requirements</strong></p>\n<p>Triaxian</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Benefits</strong></p>\n<p><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListTypes_ctl110_LabelType\">You gain a +1 trait bonus to your CMD against dragons, and whenever you encounter a particular dragon for the first time, you can make a Diplomacy check to improve its attitude toward you by a maximum of one step as a full-round action as long as you have not acted in a hostile manner toward it.</span></p>",
